headline: SMID-Cap Moats Outpace Large-Caps In August
summary: Moat Index rose 1.7%, with semis & healthcare offsetting energy headwinds. SMID Moat Index gained 3.1%, outpacing large-cap and equal-weight peers.

headline: Accenture and 5 Other AI Stocks That Don’t Stint on Dividends
summary: The Magnificent Seven yield a paltry 0.3% on average. That’s well below the S&P 500, which yields about 1.2%, or the average payout from the 400-plus dividend payers, which is closer to 2.3%.
